==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Olea
<hw>O"le*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <ety>[L. olive.
See <er>Olive</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A genus of trees
including the olive.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ The Chinese <spn>Olea fragrans</spn>, noted for its
fragrance, and the American devilwood (<spn>Olea Americana</spn>) are
now usually referred to another genus (<gen>Osmanthus</gen>).</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Oleaceae</ent>⟦br⟧
